WEBVTT

00:00:00.830 --> 00:00:03.708
It's 8:15pm in Afghanistan right now.

00:00:05.001 --> 00:00:06.502
And at this time, 10 days ago,

00:00:06.544 --> 00:00:07.712
I was sitting

00:00:07.712 --> 00:00:09.464
in an eight-foot-by-eight-foot cell

00:00:09.505 --> 00:00:10.715
in the basement

00:00:10.757 --> 00:00:12.592
of a maximum-security prison in Kabul,

00:00:12.592 --> 00:00:15.344
where I was being held captive
by the Taliban.

00:00:15.386 --> 00:00:17.555
I'd been in that cell for 104 days,

00:00:17.597 --> 00:00:20.058
and yet, I was one of the lucky ones.

00:00:22.268 --> 00:00:24.395
But I'm getting ahead of myself.

00:00:24.729 --> 00:00:26.606
Let me go back to the beginning.

00:00:28.483 --> 00:00:29.609
This is me.